name: achieve
trans: To achieve means to reach a goal or succeed in doing something.

name: benefit
trans: A benefit is something that helps or is good for you.

name: combine
trans: To combine means to mix or join things together.

name: discuss
trans: To discuss means to talk about something with others.

name: effect
trans: An effect is the result of an action or event.

name: focus
trans: To focus means to pay close attention to something.

name: gather
trans: To gather means to collect or bring together.

name: handle
trans: To handle means to deal with or take care of something.

name: improve
trans: To improve means to make something better.

name: journey
trans: A journey is a trip from one place to another.
